- **Platform-Specific**: Scripts for different platforms (LinkedIn, X/Twitter, etc.)
- **Tone Variants**: Casual, professional, value-focused
- **CTA Variants**: Different call-to-action approaches
- **Follow-up Sequences**: How to follow up if no response

