## Distribution Must Lead Validation

**CRITICAL**: Distribution strategy must be created before validation begins.

### Pre-Validation Requirements

**Before starting validation**:
1. ✅ Discovery distribution plan must exist
2. ✅ Validation distribution plan must exist
3. ✅ Top 15 communities must be identified
4. ✅ 7-14 day posting calendar must be created
5. ✅ 20 DM scripts must be ready
6. ✅ Hooks, angles, story arcs must be defined
7. ✅ Platform-specific content variants must be created

### Validation Workflow with Distribution

```
Validation Planning
  ↓
Distribution Strategy Created (MUST BE FIRST)
  ↓
Top 15 Communities Identified
  ↓
7-14 Day Posting Calendar Created
  ↓
20 DM Scripts Prepared
  ↓
Hooks, Angles, Story Arcs Defined
  ↓
Platform-Specific Content Created
  ↓
Validation Execution (Distribution Leads)
  ↓
Results Tracking
```

